Mount Akagi</b></font></font>

219
00:15:26,640 --> 00:15:30,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanna know what the difference 
is between me and the three at the top.</font>

220
00:15:30,760 --> 00:15:32,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please give me a hint, boss.</font>

221
00:15:32,990 --> 00:15:36,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fair enough. 
Hop in the passenger's seat, Sena.</font>

222
00:15:36,870 --> 00:15:38,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's been a while, 
but let's go for a ride.</font>

223
00:15:40,220 --> 00:15:42,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hold onto this for me, 
Matsumoto. Thanks.</font>

224
00:15:45,500 --> 00:15:47,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Close your eyes, Sena.</font>

225
00:15:48,850 --> 00:15:51,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But then I won't be able 
to watch you drive, boss.</font>

226
00:15:51,980 --> 00:15:53,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't try to watch.</font>

227
00:15:53,680 --> 00:15:57,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm saying shut them because 
visual information will get in the way.</font>

228
00:15:57,660 --> 00:15:59,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you want to steal my technique,</font>

229
00:15:59,920 --> 00:16:02,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you need to feel it with 
your whole body while focusing.</font>

230
00:16:04,430 --> 00:16:07,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm gonna show you 
how to tackle the roads of Akagi.</font>

231
00:16:18,510 --> 00:16:21,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is giving me serious déjà-vu.</font>

232
00:16:21,670 --> 00:16:23,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've seen this play out 
so many times before.</font>

233
00:16:24,400 --> 00:16:28,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Back then, it was Keisuke-san in the 
passenger seat, next to Ryosuke-san.</font>

234
00:16:33,610 --> 00:16:35,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The right before the hairpin.</i></font>

235
00:16:37,770 --> 00:16:41,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hitting the Akagi Downhill is so dull
 by now, I might actually fall asleep.</i></font>

236
00:16:47,570 --> 00:16:50,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The way the momentum shifts
 is so intense.</i></font>

237
00:16:50,160 --> 00:16:54,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But it goes from front to rear and left 
to right so smoothly without openings.</i></font>

238
00:16:56,070 --> 00:16:59,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's flooring it? At a time like this,
 he's going all out?</i></font>

239
00:17:00,100 --> 00:17:02,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is my boss some kind of freak?</i></font>

240
00:17:02,370 --> 00:17:05,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The speeds he's hitting, 
the way he's using his tires...</i></font>

241
00:17:06,090 --> 00:17:07,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I could go for a meal.</i></font>

242
00:17:07,890 --> 00:17:11,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's totally different. 
We're nothing alike.</i></font>

243
00:17:11,530 --> 00:17:15,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I thought I'd inherited Gunma Pride,
 and was proud to wear it,</i></font>

244
00:17:15,170 --> 00:17:17,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but this guy's on another level.</i></font>

245
00:17:19,250 --> 00:17:23,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I still have so much to learn. 
And it makes me feel like a piece of crap.</i></font>

246
00:17:26,650 --> 00:17:27,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you see now, Sena?</font>

247
00:17:27,940 --> 00:17:30,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With rear wheel drive, 
you have no choice but to floor it.</font>

248
00:17:31,040 --> 00:17:32,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The foundation of "Gunma Pride"</font>

249
00:17:32,880 --> 00:17:36,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is having the technical prowess 
to manage that permanent lead foot.</font>

250
00:17:36,730 --> 00:17:38,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And in terms of downhill racing,</font>

251
00:17:38,750 --> 00:17:41,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fujiwara Takumi would push it
even harder than I just did.</font>

252
00:17:42,120 --> 00:17:45,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The guy was a total head case, 
with more than a few screws missing.</font>

253
00:17:46,240 --> 00:17:48,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And Katagiri Kanata takes after him.</font>

254
00:17:49,270 --> 00:17:50,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leave a gap, and it's your funeral.</font>

255
00:17:51,670 --> 00:17:56,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn, boss. I'm still shaking 
from how intense that was.</font>

256
00:17:57,400 --> 00:18:00,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I gotta incorporate this into my driving 
while I've still got a feel for it.</font>

257
00:18:01,260 --> 00:18:03,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll make it mine, no matter what.</font>

258
00:18:10,200 --> 00:18:14,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aw, man. I'm here visiting old 
stomping grounds with the wife and kid.</font>

259
00:18:14,720 --> 00:18:17,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So what am I doing up 
in the mountains so late at night?</font>

260
00:18:19,170 --> 00:18:22,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Matsumoto.
 I don't know if you've heard yet,</font>

261
00:18:22,830 --> 00:18:24,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but my brother's getting married.</font>

262
00:18:25,260 --> 00:18:29,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? That's great news, 
albeit a little sudden.</font>

263
00:18:29,130 --> 00:18:30,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hadn't heard anything.</font>

264
00:18:30,580 --> 00:18:33,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He only told me about it today.</font>

265
00:18:34,090 --> 00:18:37,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the kind of big news that'll turn
 the Gunma Connection on its head.</font>

266
00:18:37,880 --> 00:18:39,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">People are gonna flip.</font>

267
00:18:40,230 --> 00:18:45,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. Nobody figured he'd do something 
as pedestrian as get married.</font>

268
00:18:46,630 --> 00:18:49,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That other ditz got married last year, too.</font>

269
00:18:50,050 --> 00:18:53,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Guess we're all getting older.</font>

270
00:18:53,710 --> 00:18:55,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if we don't always act like it.</font>

271
00:18:57,730 --> 00:19:04,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a poll on this MFG fan site about
the most exciting moment of the race.</font>

272
00:19:04,460 --> 00:19:06,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For last week's Manazuru race,</font>

273
00:19:06,270 --> 00:19:10,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the top two moments are tied.
 Isn't that something?</font>

274
00:19:10,990 --> 00:19:14,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't believe you ended up
 winning that race, Michael.</font>

275
00:19:14,370 --> 00:19:15,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Halts Maul.</font>

276
00:19:16,210 --> 00:19:20,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh dear. Looks like someone's 
in a bad mood. I wonder why.</i></font>

277
00:19:21,000 --> 00:19:26,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My aim was to run a race 
that would be boring to watch,</i></font>

278
00:19:26,060 --> 00:19:27,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and have a predictable outcome.</i></font>

279
00:19:28,380 --> 00:19:31,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What is this? Why am I so frustrated?</i></font>

280
00:19:32,110 --> 00:19:35,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>When I was battling Sawatari 
and the young driver in the 86,</i></font>

281
00:19:35,180 --> 00:19:39,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I felt a kind of excitement 
I'd never experienced before.</i></font>

282
00:19:40,630 --> 00:19:43,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It made me feel accomplished 
for winning in MFG,</i></font>

283
00:19:43,720 --> 00:19:45,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>a motorsport I'd never 
taken seriously before.</i></font>

284
00:19:46,680 --> 00:19:50,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How am I supposed 
to deal with these feelings?</i></font>

285
00:19:52,840 --> 00:19:57,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ko-kun, you should swim, too. 
The water's nice and cold.</font>

286
00:19:59,190 --> 00:20:02,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is pretty ritzy, right? 
A garden pool at a hotel in the city.</font>

287
00:20:02,960 --> 00:20:07,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bet my friends will be so jealous. 
I should post a pic and brag.</font>

288
00:20:09,170 --> 00:20:13,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sana's hips are so hot. 
She's a real find.</i></font>

289
00:20:15,170 --> 00:20:20,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it? Did you get turned on by 
how good I look in my bikini, Ko-kun?</font>

290
00:20:20,710 --> 00:20:21,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wanna head inside?</font>

291
00:20:21,950 --> 00:20:26,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, hang on. I'm not gonna 
last the day if we start this early.</font>

292
00:20:26,190 --> 00:20:28,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After all, gotta finish what we start.</font>

293
00:20:31,560 --> 00:20:36,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'll admit, thinking about it
 <i>has</i> kinda put me in the mood.</font>

294
00:20:37,240 --> 00:20:38,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Same here.</font>

295
00:20:39,100 --> 00:20:41,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Guess we should head inside.</font>

296
00:20:43,190 --> 00:20:44,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He was a busshi?</font>

297
00:20:45,320 --> 00:20:49,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The more I hear, the more a decision
 like that sounds just like Ken.</font>

298
00:20:50,160 --> 00:20:53,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I met him in a sculpting class at art school,</font>

299
00:20:53,100 --> 00:20:56,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and his works always had 
such intensity to them.</font>

300
00:20:57,860 --> 00:21:01,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Mom. There's something 
I'm wondering about.</font>

301
00:21:02,150 --> 00:21:04,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I promised Wakana and some others
 we'd go to the beach,</font>

302
00:21:04,780 --> 00:21:07,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and Kanata was supposed 
to come, too...</font>

303
00:21:07,420 --> 00:21:12,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But after everything that's happened, 
I don't think he'll be in the mood.</font>

304
00:21:12,960 --> 00:21:15,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even I'm not. Not really.</font>

305
00:21:16,080 --> 00:21:17,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you think I should cancel it?</font>

306
00:21:18,630 --> 00:21:21,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think you should go.</font>

307
00:21:21,590 --> 00:21:23,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How come?</font>

308
00:21:23,690 --> 00:21:26,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kana-chan could use a change of pace.</font>

309
00:21:26,370 --> 00:21:29,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I honestly think you should drag him along.</font>

310
00:21:29,870 --> 00:21:33,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I don't want to be a bother to him.</font>

311
00:21:33,260 --> 00:21:34,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He won't be bothered.</font>

312
00:21:34,830 --> 00:21:38,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know full well 
Kana-chan isn't like that.</font>

313
00:21:38,890 --> 00:21:43,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you think it'll help him,
 you should do it.</font>

314
00:21:43,530 --> 00:21:45,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I wonder.</i></font>

315
00:21:46,080 --> 00:21:48,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In that case, I'd better go buy a swimsuit.</i></font>

316
00:21:52,620 --> 00:21:57,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Coming to Japan may have been
 a moment of destiny for me.</i></font>

317
00:21:58,870 --> 00:22:04,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>When Mum died, 
I lost all direction in life.</i></font>

318
00:22:04,720 --> 00:22:09,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I went into my shell,
and wallowed in my solitude.</i></font>

319
00:22:10,280 --> 00:22:14,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In my loneliness, 
I may have just wanted attention.</i></font>

320
00:22:14,910 --> 00:22:16,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Like a spoiled child.</i></font>

321
00:22:18,170 --> 00:22:21,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I could've fallen into that same spiral
 after what I learned.</i></font>

322
00:22:21,600 --> 00:22:27,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But that didn't happen, Mum. 
Does that mean I've grown some?</i></font>

323
00:22:28,330 --> 00:22:34,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Here in Japan, where the people 
are so kind, I met a girl named Ren.</i></font>

324
00:22:35,070 --> 00:22:37,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She pulled me back from the brink.</i></font>

325
00:22:39,120 --> 00:22:41,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I have something important 
